{"id":"ebddbaac504037bb65d8d7b16b102f46ca6ce7dec6cc98921c3ac32a47410da7","item_id":"f0649011ab:0","text":"在 RenderMan 中渲染是通过"}
{"id":"31e97012aca2d8787395384cd2b863b88704af707168bf36a70cd70c00d71977","item_id":"f0649011ab:1","text":"ROP"}
{"id":"dc2ee850ffb55a292559941065bcff64dd7efee0c955d30e9ab2324b15ddecb8","item_id":"f0649011ab:2","text":"节点在 Houdini 中完成的。如果选择工具架按钮，我们会创建并连接常用的渲染选项，包括使用"}
{"id":"c66c3367fc146e7ab68fcb67ccdd75c3909cd0bca2343b35b4f46f0cbc0a6a52","item_id":"f0649011ab:3","text":"PxrPathTracer"}
{"id":"a75315583f6fbed0d953be3d85b3503ecf5e1ddc2c83ff5a7f1859dff8070103","item_id":"f0649011ab:4","text":"Integrator（积分器）。"}
{"id":"bc9b6d3ad367b440abbaa9d9995e0eb387b338c474ee5fb3e9419b785959b422","item_id":"f0649011ab:5","text":"渲染有很多选项，其中一些较为冷门，或只适用于特殊情况。我们支持在 Houdini 中使用多个 ROP 节点，因此你可以按任务定制每一个节点，无论是 IPR 设置、用于渲染通道的不同显示驱动（display driver），还是渲染过程中希望看到的实用调整。请务必使用你想查看其结果的那个 ROP 节点上的渲染控制。举例来说，你可以创建一个面向快速 IPR 的 ROP 节点，再创建另一个用于最终生产渲染的 ROP 节点。"}
{"id":"d2a984a33b3b1f863bda7323fcb11403dd6b54283eae208ec90f0c0b682ca4b4","item_id":"f0649011ab:6","text":"本文档旨在帮助你尽可能简单地理解这些差异。"}
{"id":"f9a281028d706068df353b8a0d5dd5556df912136c63ea1f7ff070ba9373cf01","item_id":"f0649011ab:7","text":"关于为合成提供 AOVs 和 LPE 内容的信息，请参见"}
{"id":"ad62b458148faa26adfe6b443e70dcbff6d6c64e4e88658ed90e302f774a1d2b","item_id":"f0649011ab:8","text":"AOVs 页面。"}
{"id":"899792ddd294a84d2d4c05f0070abbd44aff8fd403b41679131fd7be0a3a026b","item_id":"f0649011ab:9","text":"关于 Driver 选项卡以及渲染到设备的信息可参见"}
{"id":"fcec91509759ad995c2cd14bcb26b2720993faf61c29d379b270d442d92290eb","item_id":"f0649011ab:10","text":"此处"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"f0649011ab:11","text":"。"}
{"id":"65c2266b8192fb70f1450960af784381525e5b8d041b05290713db3238cb846c","item_id":"f0649011ab:12","text":"标准控制"}
{"id":"d452583a74d0e772db89d8f783831098869148222427750bedecc4a1b50380b5","item_id":"f0649011ab:13","text":"按钮"}
{"id":"54da129c439f65729dc9740302496086ea9f69486e340b7d0765902c5afc2ebf","item_id":"f0649011ab:14","text":"Render（渲染）："}
{"id":"15562787385409b880fd5dcc44c725fcdc09e3160b0ec2cf538f9145b476c126","item_id":"f0649011ab:15","text":"启动到 RenderMan 的交互式渲染"}
{"id":"794ae8de1e5c97d2a8ecd44299cc03cd35cf2e161e88bf1793c3c6b5898d003d","item_id":"f0649011ab:16","text":"Stop（停止）："}
{"id":"edbacf51d2e9595ed757a1f3c5cfcc8755071aa20ab9a30662fc1ce6c15d3f1e","item_id":"f0649011ab:17","text":"取消或结束交互式渲染 (也可以从"}
{"id":"fd202218d7579c6e27ee390288d7ed59c5fdaca13a01272f0813c6cf1340ad0c","item_id":"f0649011ab:18","text":"/wiki/spaces/REN20/pages/21561593"}
{"id":"80ff4a75274b09d819e55fd722051be191453da8864edf54d08bbc8145f7c81e","item_id":"f0649011ab:19","text":"Render in Background（后台渲染）："}
{"id":"9ee7c46d895480df13e0d93b17733b97c9586a05d6de64c64acb9143d3b04b57","item_id":"f0649011ab:20","text":"在保持 Houdini UI 可用的同时进行渲染"}
{"id":"acb944295d3405450ca7a72a260022e848320bc50a5695d90df57715ff891073","item_id":"f0649011ab:21","text":"View Rib（查看 Rib）："}
{"id":"d76ca348035234969e6f8ec9dcb913bdb8c79b8c6f345bc54d1dd5a73e0d655d","item_id":"f0649011ab:22","text":"导出 RIB 文件 (默认位置为你的 .hip 场景文件所在位置)。默认使用 Binary 以节省空间。你可以在 RIB 选项卡中更改此设置"}
{"id":"48b87c2d2f6f535adf7c5ccf5ec2962c426a3ce97f721a8cd2940fe8e18e63f3","item_id":"f0649011ab:23","text":"Bake（烘焙）："}
{"id":"ed155e3cbc5f82961d524b6b43436541e381fdf65a147e22a8f27eb4a43caad8","item_id":"f0649011ab:24","text":"运行一次烘焙渲染，用于"}
{"id":"b23fc6d663cf11b0e0af899929f4464007efd769bef2e6d592854ae5c689f4c6","item_id":"f0649011ab:25","text":"bake pattern（烘焙 pattern）"}
{"id":"a19db4951fbcd4cb71abf080d03aa174e0e0a821085e70159975abe4f1c32c4a","item_id":"f0649011ab:26","text":"网络"}
{"id":"321719a4efe962f75a3d8facca41897ef97186ced54e18c758612cac537afa4c","item_id":"f0649011ab:27","text":"Controls...（控制...）："}
{"id":"553a2624b8ebbb6e01680513b450451930ea39db862def45978c2b466739b863","item_id":"f0649011ab:28","text":"用于渲染的附加选项，例如质量覆盖和帧设置"}
{"id":"f7d51b086fac702e03eb17bdce29451d1bb6d2deba592ddb2e52ab2b46ee0929","item_id":"f0649011ab:29","text":"常用选择"}
{"id":"6d202ac3cd0adaa4fd1fcb84a3312c047e425611afc7cb5cb96508bcdd5dcc69","item_id":"f0649011ab:30","text":"Valid Frame Range（有效帧范围）："}
{"id":"ffa0eb124b570827de35d2ec998cf644d7759c608c6f7130c2dcba80c077f9db","item_id":"f0649011ab:31","text":"选择要渲染的帧；对交互式渲染无效"}
{"id":"158bdebdeeeb556b85e092534455e571e84d93375a056a0fad0b1d1f8235dd85","item_id":"f0649011ab:32","text":"Start/End/Inc（起始/结束/增量）："}
{"id":"037448da180ab2d138b554c0e59f26dfd20d82e1d506f3b8270d600cc90e1f77","item_id":"f0649011ab:33","text":"帧范围和增量，接受浮点值"}
{"id":"c56620a65582f55f3d7e265ab0e204858a38732de75de483eb1d2e041cad84e9","item_id":"f0649011ab:34","text":"Render With Take（使用 Take 渲染）："}
{"id":"b1ac8338d389d7b3c1e1e16e999b5de9ad78921eea612da6274345eed4fb4545","item_id":"f0649011ab:35","text":"要使用的版本"}
{"id":"9185a900aa8d1263b0f5bff1d8f28363f5509d96c0b0371b651ed1df14a374e7","item_id":"f0649011ab:36","text":"Camera（摄影机）："}
{"id":"8a7eeb38cbfccc23ba1946fe0d6dd7c67811829c53043ca3b1dc8287741c7d28","item_id":"f0649011ab:37","text":"Path（路径）指向用于渲染的所选摄影机。必须指定一个摄影机。如果使用我们的工具架按钮，我们会填充该字段"}
{"id":"98e1fa3be43d5c3d6c59fa49c0a31b1fa8135df836584a14ad6bb7de10824c5f","item_id":"f0649011ab:38","text":"Override Camera Resolution（覆盖摄影机分辨率）："}
{"id":"255fa07e4d7a6eb78a1b34c5d600301bf95de919148d313ba78784ae847439fe","item_id":"f0649011ab:39","text":"将渲染分辨率从摄影机设置中指定的分辨率改为此处的设置"}
{"id":"e2fe353986e6111a3a2601120eec7fb5e01e2de468cbc28a783a5db8765a8f2c","item_id":"f0649011ab:40","text":"渲染"}
{"id":"0895d7a557385be92503e1e65e72457d8e15dc918b53b961eaeed33b4830dbda","item_id":"f0649011ab:41","text":"Integrator（积分器）："}
{"id":"f8cf83a76a98df2dd4799b4d0d4f6ffc9af9a3a72d8648f94ca7cdea4b52fde7","item_id":"f0649011ab:42","text":"要使用哪个"}
{"id":"168196d133817ed25c3fe0bf9a5254309ab899daa622e81d3ead0daf0eb33def","item_id":"f0649011ab:43","text":"积分器"}
{"id":"a2861a048c2cb60cb7f3506d76d49866be5befd4de1f118ea2f3690d77654939","item_id":"f0649011ab:44","text":"。如果此项为空或未设置，则使用"}
{"id":"b8a3a7debba3ac57d77b99dd1e29c9928852324cf3e57bca1387c9e0afdf766e","item_id":"f0649011ab:45","text":"PxrDefault"}
{"id":"e43f447b65e6b1236fa237ffc613d5e0dde3509a5d3089e6378686e41318d17a","item_id":"f0649011ab:46","text":"Integrator（积分器）"}
{"id":"a09f6df9dc866d1f4b70d9dd1ac932acf55140eb8645eec42c5ff515bffe0e0e","item_id":"f0649011ab:47","text":"Enable Depth of Field（启用景深）："}
{"id":"15dad079b76f54744ee4eda7baed3742d15145dd871af4433c47b21137877268","item_id":"f0649011ab:48","text":"允许使用 Depth of Field（景深）设置；如果你在调整场景时想暂时禁用景深，这是一个简单的开关"}
{"id":"3196aeaa8cffd951d7abf8adfc6dc462fc77c6e47255c144e7bff744191e92cd","item_id":"f0649011ab:49","text":"Allow Motion Blur（允许运动模糊）："}
{"id":"6f9170c5e277afb091e9b56498228667637a3fee0607f1c37085cac3fcbf69c8","item_id":"f0649011ab:50","text":"为场景实体开启运动模糊。请注意，体积的运动模糊由 BxDF,"}
{"id":"6b2b3cbd4ad476016050e61b781d1112117b06945fb578fbffcfc4ff3f6daa69","item_id":"f0649011ab:51","text":"PxrVolume"}
{"id":"dcb1661cdedc0df5f9c7be9a6c047f36d437ed7fdac442e7f058d6eafb848c08","item_id":"f0649011ab:52","text":"单独控制"}
{"id":"8298788494e15c42fcf66cce376d99470ffaab5132663ada3a8c6e88bf0b39bc","item_id":"f0649011ab:53","text":"Sampling Tab（采样选项卡）"}
{"id":"2fa97693b70fa87b95b2d1bdf9558e4ac65d5e82d145f13a03849c4d9c4957a9","item_id":"f0649011ab:54","text":"另请参见"}
{"id":"de1c6e91aafdb7443e67f5fdab725e493b01ba048ff63082b12c271b6bd02886","item_id":"f0649011ab:55","text":"Renderer Options（渲染器选项）"}
{"id":"4c7148e466d4434d1a1411c15f757ec78ba8f3ef4b6210d4a156bc3aaa6e71e5","item_id":"f0649011ab:56","text":"了解更多细节"}
{"id":"9658523eec5f91a482a8266a0be1a0565f4e08a3df1817215f2102226b339b0d","item_id":"f0649011ab:57","text":"Incremental（增量）："}
{"id":"813eb7c93b4904e86ac36d31a990da90fda723f64cb94f65456cbb09058d5c84","item_id":"f0649011ab:58","text":"渲染帧级 pass，而不是基于 bucket/tile 的渲染。对于大多数渲染选择都更推荐使用它，包括批处理和"}
{"id":"b03e5ef82c5cd44401ab2cf9d40091fed5de947a69439f2a43cf2059195a56e4","item_id":"f0649011ab:59","text":"带检查点的"}
{"id":"f875598edc8d8270e7c98b6d7a652cac9e91a2abdc8ba7db2f7a4362566985e5","item_id":"f0649011ab:60","text":"渲染。"}
{"id":"5118a820f3b887113b3c881add7b51aed22eb5f986cf5a843aa0c2c0926444b9","item_id":"f0649011ab:61","text":"Adaptive Metric（自适应度量）："}
{"id":"520f87e0a3f648e6e5c1f58096e365c849bd5b5089634966996ffd25815163ca","item_id":"f0649011ab:62","text":"选择"}
{"id":"8302d697acc497c2afce0b6152ffbe289ee27e7c7fcf42be6770d45067f74d80","item_id":"f0649011ab:63","text":"采样方法"}
{"id":"679729066d4bfdaeff71e708551c3fd8cee2bbf33bff54f766b0c07174d47d85","item_id":"f0649011ab:64","text":"供自适应采样器使用"}
{"id":"a830916d4c955f6397d05dc18bb68662f6f30245158caa49d03faf7a583277a7","item_id":"f0649011ab:65","text":"Exposure Bracket (variance)（曝光包围，variance）："}
{"id":"82d3b82a8d1637309efe9fe50e657c328fd08e6ecb0817a14762ceb1c7c1f750","item_id":"f0649011ab:66","text":"最小曝光包围用于确定最大强度；超过该强度后，任何强度方差、对比或差异在视觉上都不再重要。另外，最大曝光包围用于确定在假设合成结果位于此范围内时，为得到最大导数需要沿 gamma 校正曲线向下走多远。"}
{"id":"f272c0069aa9b982a2ac57be5bca5141fa19561acd5d4c7130de9c8a28089d74","item_id":"f0649011ab:67","text":"Dark Falloff (contrast)（暗部衰减，contrast）："}
{"id":"11e86818231673d17bf2b689b7dc186147042eeefbf20cd1d8972c81f0d9e4af","item_id":"f0649011ab:68","text":"如果图像中的某个区域暗于此阈值，则停止采样，因为它将不可见或难以被感知"}
{"id":"06a14192e28b1800ab64070207623af992ffe3ec157806b7eb70260849872c55","item_id":"f0649011ab:69","text":"Pixel Variance（像素方差）："}
{"id":"68573a1a8e4f5dbe15f549af45993bd398a78f51f27dceb2061ba18607dd7ec7","item_id":"f0649011ab:70","text":"这是渲染的主要质量控制。值越低，质量越高。典型生产设置为 0.01 到 0.005（极高质量）。根据场景复杂度，0.015 通常是较好的中等质量设置。"}
{"id":"57c3b172de004cc313cd1e08b01e49878e4b841788b51f61226e283028697ce6","item_id":"f0649011ab:71","text":"Interactive Refinement（交互式细化）："}
{"id":"c867167d20359a149466db78e82a2279b7bba8835289c23caaa491ecef5bf652","item_id":"f0649011ab:72","text":"在交互式渲染中，渲染器被允许以多激进的方式对一帧进行粗略采样。数值越高，在收敛前越激进、越模糊。"}
{"id":"e41f08d35dd171fae766527304b84b79f457573cc418526128c3d861bc1c31e0","item_id":"f0649011ab:73","text":"Sampling（采样）"}
{"id":"1d79fa83f53b965cecffc1dd93a91f8819008cdd2b3c1243987289e2a1d33bb8","item_id":"f0649011ab:74","text":"Minimum Samples（最小采样数）："}
{"id":"dc0b379bf88c0d120da65a5af70d98e1b334925453c6c9c5e184cdf426381d2a","item_id":"f0649011ab:75","text":"每个像素所需的最低采样数。值为 0 时，会取 Maximum Samples 设置的最接近平方根。为了捕捉小型图像特征，例如小 particles（粒子）或细发丝，可能需要更高的数值。"}
{"id":"bd0af89b0cc612c6f637bdcc4c4a98ad56c02d97f3cca8223549f7f27483bf72","item_id":"f0649011ab:76","text":"Extra Minimum Samples（额外最小采样数）："}
{"id":"016ae67205644114366e92db899f58fb7bd0f4293ee905d4f469c649cd672fdc","item_id":"f0649011ab:77","text":"如果某个像素未通过方差测试，此值会在再次测试方差前强制增加指定数量的采样。为 0 时，默认使用与 Minimum Samples 相同的数量。"}
{"id":"d36e27767d808ba6beeb3559a74eaa149ca7cd3352ffd33054fd080d946153bd","item_id":"f0649011ab:78","text":"Maximum Samples（最大采样数）："}
{"id":"8274e89c41530d87046d79be44b8af33ce2c183cfffb846ed5d91b5ea7d31e8f","item_id":"f0649011ab:79","text":"在停止对一个像素采样之前，我们会采用的最多采样数。渲染景深、运动模糊或其他噪声较大的效果时，可能需要更高的数值。"}
{"id":"d0c21e85d32218cf75853ac71fba34d0f51f1472d5b6d87416e8c429261f4a15","item_id":"f0649011ab:80","text":"Adapt All（适应全部）："}
{"id":"96045a008b6b196615803648b17bc85a24b45872ff165c7540f0e7db0ffe5a2b","item_id":"f0649011ab:81","text":"将所有 AOVs 都与方差阈值进行测试。这意味着 AOVs 更可能没有噪声，但会显著增加渲染时间，因为某些 AOVs 可能触发更多采样，却对图像质量提升不大。"}
{"id":"0e01ef0dbc7d13b03ace279cafc427b4131daa2b95a4a7e466b9bb25892dec62","item_id":"f0649011ab:82","text":"Pixel Filter Mode（像素滤波模式）"}
{"id":"2494378acc0036f97c6f7960499540a80f6bc4d4865f8dbc971b589030b783ff","item_id":"f0649011ab:83","text":"Weighted（加权）："}
{"id":"fb36e3b1ddfc4b3fc416ee622d3cf049b51039b8712a05409aa26c704e124f4e","item_id":"f0649011ab:84","text":"采样会一起滤波。仅在 RIS 中支持。"}
{"id":"38c51805b8720d2378b55016fc44f9be49232c327346c08ce523ef7ee49cc391","item_id":"f0649011ab:85","text":"Importance（重要性）："}
{"id":"259882f3fd6909fc44d519b1d088a48f144a749d19a6fc6b1201146ffafd6eca","item_id":"f0649011ab:86","text":"像素彼此独立。这是降噪应用所必需的，包括 Optix 和 RenderMan 的交互式机器学习降噪器。"}
{"id":"6a40345fb297889168c5ab8ce6dff5e8d3948fd96c3e4c9f1825ddeb518def3c","item_id":"f0649011ab:87","text":"Sample Offset（采样偏移）："}
{"id":"f9bf910c5ac1c4aee422fe15e5890cc7f7e6f1a4afc0a337bbd0e4dddb231e99","item_id":"f0649011ab:88","text":"允许并行渲染多张图像（使用不同的 sampleoffset 值），然后再将它们合成"}
{"id":"5c89485bbbeacbbee5290096b49889f9800c5e0fb211640721fdb64a39e1afa3","item_id":"f0649011ab:89","text":"Extreme Motion/DOF（极端运动/景深）："}
{"id":"d04853130fcc38e85e4ac5dafc3d78e61c16eec2a1520abcba844804e6a72215","item_id":"f0649011ab:90","text":"当景深或运动模糊在图像中极端或占主导时，改变采样技术。这更准确，但会带来一些额外开销。"}
{"id":"e08ad2f46b9070dc8fd728e68c59b4ed89370b5a7d3c5a499f86f059d8cd7187","item_id":"f0649011ab:91","text":"Default Ray Depth（默认射线深度）："}
{"id":"863ae5e127effd16f6e39a5324c45ecd9609fb491acbb1b96fcebf96b8c3a7df","item_id":"f0649011ab:92","text":"默认"}
{"id":"32a856b02e332d5af28faeaa2fdbcee3f06f1845481bc5fb5e0585e4456fbf80","item_id":"f0649011ab:93","text":"深度"}
{"id":"f9399f6f267c3493acf1c5582d3176434fff6f2d10e928b45a66dbcfecb184aa","item_id":"f0649011ab:94","text":"按散射类型（diffuse 或 specular）全局应用到场景中的所有对象。Object attributes（对象属性）可以覆盖此值，但不能覆盖 Integrator 的 Max Depth。"}
{"id":"e1146f006ab341fd87d71cf0d913bba2253c28dfc51831688ae938bd01dcd7f5","item_id":"f0649011ab:95","text":"Filter（滤波器）："}
{"id":"04c8e4690d1391aa8bd6d26f6636a526dfbbedafeb62bfa85da4e91ffb4d4438","item_id":"f0649011ab:96","text":"父图像滤波器的类型和窗口大小；默认的 Gaussian 2.0 2.0 通常适用于绝大多数情况。"}
{"id":"495acbf9ec2c90cb4e36d217cd2435571ec1fa351cc3053c14403ee124e6bb44","item_id":"f0649011ab:97","text":"着色"}
