{"id":"af45f1b5158fea47b3e7a5e0c01b090425c32f9463f7c8ec0911ed76c595a13a","item_id":"f0649011ab:107","text":"原始默认值，使用你的场景网格作为场景原点"}
{"id":"ceb6666dbcce39f395676b957b0783bda2dc6c5a3797b7473f8dd41cce1f7e21","item_id":"f0649011ab:108","text":"World Offset（世界偏移）："}
{"id":"37af9865faddfe1e843382917d0dad741fdbfcff02202916cf60925ce84ffb62","item_id":"f0649011ab:109","text":"用户提供的坐标，用作渲染期间场景的新原点"}
{"id":"ceb6666dbcce39f395676b957b0783bda2dc6c5a3797b7473f8dd41cce1f7e21","item_id":"f0649011ab:110","text":"World Offset（世界偏移）："}
{"id":"92b3d5ab09926cdee1e16fa17c6bc945dad36a5e6c8379168fd5fa493fe2ce4d","item_id":"f0649011ab:111","text":"如果上面选择了 World Offset，则此处为新的场景原点的用户定义位置"}
{"id":"4d18be7c1134f66586fc46c51b3d8bf4d1449c76ee5eae7e618adf1c0c638a12","item_id":"f0649011ab:112","text":"Light Learning Scheme（灯光学习方案）："}
{"id":"ac769213123ee242e3ae88f98a72bb61e9e47168987bca3df001fb83e65d7d68","item_id":"f0649011ab:113","text":"此选项允许渲染器利用灯光属性、位置和遮挡信息，告知渲染器如何在场景中平衡采样以改善收敛。复杂场景比简单场景或灯光很少的场景受益更多。"}
{"id":"8207c3e696faee53aa05459a7b167730e5acad02f3c955236123b2c443501718","item_id":"f0649011ab:114","text":"Light Learning 可能会带来显著的内存成本。"}
{"id":"6d89eb7d0938564938636b4a5ee73c09e55c2e6e5aaa9e3016781bf54805e8d3","item_id":"f0649011ab:115","text":"Render（渲染）"}
